<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一年之計在於春，<delay frames="40" />
可不能因為現在是新年期間，<delay20 />
就開始暴飲暴食啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和大家一起享受佳節氣氛很好，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己在家裡悠哉度日也不錯。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每個人的新年假期都有各自不同的美好呢！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年一開始我就很走運喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為能像這樣見到你，<delay20 />
還能跟你說話<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你是會去新年參拜的那種人嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我偶爾會思考<delay20 />
神明們真的存在嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起神明，<delay20 />
我可能更想見到自己吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了重新檢視自己的內心，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前聽了廣播節目上<delay20 />
關於今年運勢的占卜<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到我居然是大凶啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過 No Problem！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我擁有你的陪伴啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>